{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"18991a69-4a85-42dc-8a3a-0d77d7b6df67","content":"I don't have a skill available for **analyzing** crash dumps — the tools I have are focused on **collecting** dumps and symbolicating mobile crash logs.\n\nHere's how you can analyze your `.dmp` file:\n\n### Recommended Tools\n\n1. **`dotnet-dump analyze`** (cross-platform):\n   ```bash\n   dotnet tool install -g dotnet-dump\n   dotnet-dump analyze your-file.dmp\n   ```\n   Useful commands inside the REPL:\n   - `clrstack` — managed call stack\n   - `pe` — print last exception\n   - `dumpheap -stat` — heap summary\n   - `threads` — list all threads\n\n2. **WinDbg** (Windows, most powerful):\n   - Load the dump, then `.loadby sos clr` (Framework) or `.loadby sos coreclr` (modern .NET)\n   - `!analyze -v` for automatic crash analysis\n\n3. **Visual Studio** (Windows):\n   - File → Open → File → select the `.dmp`\n   - Click \"Debug with Managed Only\"\n\n### Quick Start\n\nIf you have `dotnet-dump` available on this machine and can upload the `.dmp` file here, I can run the analysis commands for you. Would you like to try that?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"50ba452e-0167-4c2b-b196-74b2a31b7781","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a .dmp crash dump file from a .NET application and wants to analyze it. Let me look at the available skills to see if any can help with this.\n\nLooking at the available skills:\n- `dump-collect` - This is for *collecting* crash dumps, not analyzing them. The description explicitly says \"DO NOT USE FOR: analyzing or debugging dumps, post-mortem investigation with lldb/windbg/dotnet-dump analyze\"\n- `android-tombstone-symbolication` - For Android tombstone files, not .dmp files\n- `apple-crash-symbolication` - For Apple .ips crash logs, not .dmp files\n\n\n- `dotnet-trace-collect` - For capturing diagnostic artifacts, not analyzing dumps\n\nNone of the available skills are designed for analyzing .dmp files, so I'll need to provide guidance on how to approach this manually.","outputTokens":512,"requestId":"7643:31275C:EA7C18:1124818:69FE93A4"},"id":"ed68a0ab-e811-4f70-a488-644710aa763c","timestamp":"2026-05-09T01:53:54.045Z","parentId":"f71995ff-0973-4630-9294-027cf9748ca5"}
